    a: 'Most platforms charge 2.9-3.5% for credit cards and 0.8-1.2% for ACH/bank transfers. Jobber charges 2.9% + $0.30 for cards, while Housecall Pro is 3.2% + $0.30. Enterprise solutions like ServiceTitan often have negotiable rates starting at 2.5%.' 
