    q: 'Do HVAC invoicing tools integrate with my accounting software?', 
    a: 'Most modern invoicing platforms sync with QuickBooks, Xero, and other accounting software. Jobber and Housecall Pro both offer real-time QuickBooks sync, while ServiceTitan includes built-in accounting features that eliminate the need for separate software.' 
  },
  { 
    q: 'What payment methods should my invoicing software accept?', 
    a: 'Essential payment methods include credit/debit cards, ACH bank transfers, and mobile payments like Apple Pay. Top platforms also support payment plans and financing options, which can increase your average job value by 15-25%.' 
  },
  { 
    q: 'How much faster do customers pay with automated invoicing?', 
    a: 'HVAC contractors using automated invoicing get paid 8-15 days faster on average. Immediate mobile invoicing with payment links reduces payment time from 30+ days to 15-20 days, improving cash flow significantly for seasonal businesses.' 
  }
];
